  ('social-worker-moex-01896', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '相關文獻指出：「當家庭的情緒系統失去功能，孩子從小遭受虐待或目睹暴力，沒有機會學習正向的情 緒管理，反而學習到以暴力發洩情緒的行為模式」。若依據此觀點進行目睹兒成年後暴力傾向之研究， 請問這是屬於那一種探究的方式？', '["應用法", "轉換法", "歸納法", "演繹法"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f540dda9f6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b6e329770714", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01897', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果我們知道變項A發生的時間在變項B之前，那麼我們可以很肯定地說下列何者是正確的？', '["變項A是變項B的原因", "變項A不是變項B的原因", "變項B是變項A的原因", "變項B不是變項A的原因"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f540dda9f6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b6e329770714", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
